<topic id='element_organisation_identifier__code_of_commissioner_.description'>
  <title>Description</title>
  <titlealts>
    <searchtitle>Data Element: ORGANISATION IDENTIFIER (CODE OF COMMISSIONER) - Description</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>
  <div>
      <p>
         <xref outputclass="element"
               keyref="element_organisation_identifier__code_of_commissioner_">ORGANISATION IDENTIFIER (CODE OF COMMISSIONER)</xref>
 is the same as attribute 
              <xref outputclass="attribute" keyref="attribute_organisation_identifier">ORGANISATION IDENTIFIER</xref>.        </p>
      <p>
         <xref outputclass="element"
               keyref="element_organisation_identifier__code_of_commissioner_">ORGANISATION IDENTIFIER (CODE OF COMMISSIONER)</xref>
 is the 
              <xref outputclass="attribute" keyref="attribute_organisation_identifier">ORGANISATION IDENTIFIER</xref>
 of the 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_organisation">ORGANISATION</xref>
 commissioning health care.        </p>
      <p>
For 
              <xref href="https://v3.datadictionary.nhs.uk/web_site_content/navigation/commissioning_data_sets_menu.html"
               scope="external"
               format="html">Commissioning Data Sets</xref>, the 
              <xref outputclass="element"
               keyref="element_organisation_identifier__code_of_commissioner_">ORGANISATION IDENTIFIER (CODE OF COMMISSIONER)</xref>
 should always be the 
              <xref outputclass="attribute" keyref="attribute_organisation_identifier">ORGANISATION IDENTIFIER</xref>
 of the original commissioner to support the 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
               keyref="supporting_definition_national_tariff_payment_system">National Tariff Payment System</xref>.        </p>
      <p>
The 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_nhs_england">NHS England</xref>
 document 
              <xref href="https://www.england.nhs.uk/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/who-pays.pdf"
               scope="external"
               format="html">"Who pays? Determining responsibility for payments to providers"</xref>
 sets out a framework for establishing responsibility for commissioning an individual's care within the NHS, (i.e. determining who pays for a 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENT</xref>'s care.)        </p>
      <p>The document includes information on the following:</p>
      <ul>
         <li>
            <div>
               <p>General Rules</p>
            </div>
         </li>
         <li>
            <div>
               <p>
Applying the rules to 
                                <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                        keyref="business_definition_clinical_commissioning_group">Clinical Commissioning Group</xref>
 and 
                                <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                        keyref="business_definition_nhs_england">NHS England</xref>
 commissioned services                    </p>
            </div>
         </li>
         <li>
            <div>
               <p>Exceptions to the general rules</p>
            </div>
         </li>
         <li>
            <div>
               <p>
Examples to help clarify the boundaries of responsibility between commissioning 
                                <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_organisation">ORGANISATIONS</xref>.                    </p>
            </div>
         </li>
      </ul>
      <p>
For further information on this document contact 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_nhs_england">NHS England</xref>
 at 
              <xref href="https://www.england.nhs.uk/contact-us/"
               scope="external"
               format="html">"Contact us"</xref>.        </p>
      <p>
Where 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_nhs_england">NHS England</xref>
 is the responsible commissioner for a specialised 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_service">SERVICE</xref>, based on the 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_nhs_england">NHS England</xref>
         <xref href="https://www.england.nhs.uk/publication/commissioner-assignment-method-flowchart-201617/"
               scope="external"
               format="html">Commissioner Assignment Method (CAM)</xref>, one of the 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_specialised_commissioning_hub">Specialised Commissioning Hub</xref>
 
              <xref outputclass="attribute" keyref="attribute_organisation_identifier">ORGANISATION IDENTIFIERS</xref>
 should be used depending on which 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_health_care_provider">Health Care Provider</xref>
 delivered the 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_service">SERVICE</xref>, e.g. 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_nhs_trust">NHS Trust</xref>, 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_independent_sector_healthcare_provider">Independent Sector Healthcare Provider</xref>.        </p>
      <p>
The 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_nhs_digital">NHS Digital</xref>
 website provides a mapping list of which 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_health_care_provider">Health Care Providers</xref>
 map to which 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_specialised_commissioning_hub">Specialised Commissioning Hub</xref>. The mapping can be found on the 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
               keyref="supporting_definition_organisation_data_service">Organisation Data Service</xref>
 web pages at: 
              <xref href="https://digital.nhs.uk/services/organisation-data-service/data-downloads/other-nhs-organisations"
               scope="external"
               format="html">Provider to Commissioning Hub Mapping</xref>.        </p>
      <p>
         <b>
            <xref outputclass="element"
                  keyref="element_organisation_code__code_of_commissioner_">ORGANISATION CODE (CODE OF COMMISSIONER)</xref>
 will be replaced with 
                  <xref outputclass="element"
                  keyref="element_organisation_identifier__code_of_commissioner_">ORGANISATION IDENTIFIER (CODE OF COMMISSIONER)</xref>, when it has been approved for use in national information standards.            </b>
      </p>
  </div>
